{"tid":2018942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［SaveHK] 藍屍對後生仔自殺既睇法","createTime":"2020-05-16T02:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T02:56:49.000Z","uid":127033,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7aff2f2b679d68cd74691df7d20530af9af7bba7","tid":2018942,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T02:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vdr8hRe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVdr8hRe.png&h=65e7babc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又係我細個我以前乜乜柒柒啲口吻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />噁心到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講以為你識個細路知佢發生乜事，事實就係你呢啲社會垃圾咁樣既思想令社會多左份壓力<br />\n不意外，睇野全面有腦都唔會做藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb854f904088e6be788260f2c1a6f3b57a6d7c91","tid":2018942,"uid":213037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T02:53:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Task1 Task2 Task3  Like retweet reply</span><br />\nTwitter 戰線手足整咗個網站出嚟比大家做task<br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/twitter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Ftwitter&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexofxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=600f138a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/twitter</a><br />\n<br />\n入bot 拎任務24小時更新：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexofxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=e387755d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n另有手足會係佢Twitter Account 每日更新任務:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTweetingforHK&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexofxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=bef4ed14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK</a><br />\n<br />\n或者download 香城online 個app 都有Twitter 任務做<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHKOnlinePortal&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexofxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=8e3c175f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal</a><br />\n<br />\nLike retweet reply<br />\n*如果見到想用嘅圖已經有手足用咗請搵第二張圖<br />\n*如果見到已經有好多圖就唔好再放圖，只留文字（短短地都得）<br />\n*唔好只係扔低張圖咩字都唔打<br />\n*唔知留咩好就like 手足留言或者啲對我哋有利嘅留言<br />\n<br />\n將Twitter 變成日常，每人每日做少少。<br />\n每人嘅一小步加埋就係一大步。<br />\n我哋唔知做咩先有用，所以咩都試下咩都做下"},{"pid":"a01432950dca1c81c01284e27f8d679ac68b1f18","tid":2018942,"uid":13503,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T02:54:03.000Z","msg":"藍屍就係缺乏同理心嘅人亦都係恐怖殺手嘅特徵"},{"pid":"fb6658499fb06014208a5d9cdd3d15d76de26370","tid":2018942,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a01432950dca1c81c01284e27f8d679ac68b1f18","tid":2018942,"uid":13503,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T02:54:03.000Z","msg":"藍屍就係缺乏同理心嘅人亦都係恐怖殺手嘅特徵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T02:56:15.000Z","msg":"係，個個都賊眉賊眼咁，真係反映晒係個樣度"},{"pid":"ba89f66c191d90b49a830c63548bf0cef59d9ff2","tid":2018942,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T02:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死咗咁多手足都無可疑<br />\n無家長做野你就知啲藍屍係咩心態<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"}]}